{"tid":594064,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇爸打都試過屋企搵到條唔屬於自己頭髮","createTime":"2018-03-15T13:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T14:05:07.000Z","uid":5584,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4ca0f50e510df70040bc7669837829ac3dc7b1f7","tid":594064,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"好奇怪<br />\n我同條女都係黑色頭髮<br />\n但係我竟然響張床度搵到條金色頭髮<br />\n我覺得奇怪就問女朋友<br />\n女朋友都表示好奇怪<br />\n佢就話幫手google一下<br />\n一陣之後就同我講話網上有文章講話頭髮脫落後<br />\n如果天氣潮濕<br />\n好快就會變金色<br />\n仲話唔信可以「蚊」我條陰毛試下<br />\n我心諗你無端端「蚊」我條陰毛一定有陰謀<br />\n算鳩數繼續玩MHW<br />\n現在越諗越覺得奇怪<br />\n請問有冇爸打都試過啲毛無端端變金色？"},{"pid":"d2836a5931ed9c7ad8f4257d6655ad256218945a","tid":594064,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:48:27.000Z","msg":"自稱02最強既厹<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/593940/page/4?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/593940/page/4?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7c71826ae7f1c57deabe9f4dc3947f2c9810cfa1","tid":594064,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2836a5931ed9c7ad8f4257d6655ad256218945a","tid":594064,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:48:27.000Z","msg":"自稱02最強既厹<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/593940/page/4?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/593940/page/4?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"通常小學雞先用CMHK<br />\n你冇錢出返個似樣啲嘅Plan咩？"},{"pid":"a15f91885403d2b8ca4fae4dc1c7167b3695077a","tid":594064,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:53:25.000Z","msg":"知唔知上手住戶咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb55fe99807962fe634501cffbe4f9c368a41a2","tid":594064,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:53:49.0